{"tid":1689573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自由行無向狗狗企直，所以比狗狗亂棍打鳩","createTime":"2019-11-03T01:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T01:58:42.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0dc8d80f7b6a78817305a155b028cb7d8788ee2a","tid":1689573,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:27:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191103/60225017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191103%2F60225017&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=927fe9b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191103%2F60225017&h=eab0d02f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191103/60225017</a><br />\n<br />\n港島區原定有兩個獲警發出不反對通知書的集會，以及區議會選舉候選人根據法例舉辦的聚會，但全數均被警方「終止」，港島區就由和平集會演變成警民衝突，晚上示威者散去後仍有大批防暴警進行搜捕。晚上接近凌晨，有一對男女於銅鑼灣被警員截查，在搜查隨身物品及搜身後未發現異常，<strong>但該名男子在搜查接近完成後將身體挨住石壆，被警喝止「唔好反抗」，然後就將該名男子拘捕並帶走。 <br />\n<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n事發於將晚上11時45分，當時大批防暴警於銅鑼灣皇室堡對出，當時現場並無黑衣人，而警方就在附近截查青年，一對男女成為防暴警截查對象，該對男女被帶到石壆附近搜身及搜查隨身物品，整個搜查過程約數分鐘，有女警將物品逐一放回袋內。<strong>片段清楚見到該名男子袋中為日常用品，而該名男子亦不時與警員對談，男子一直無與警員有接觸，防暴警亦無壓止該名男子。不過在搜查完畢後，男子欲將身體挨往石壆方向，數名防暴警隨即喝止，並捉住該名男子高呼「唔好反抗」、「唔好使用武力」，同時將該名男子拘捕，男子身往後挨，穩住身子再站起，即時有防暴警衝前，由上而下向被捕男子的頭方向扑去，最後十多名防暴警將該名購物男帶上警車。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">該名男子來自內地的女友人事後接受傳媒訪問時表示，該名男子是她男友，她表示當時正準備回家，被男友拖着走，然後就被警員截查，對話警察突然拘捕男友表示不明白，也不知道男友到哪間警署，而警員亦無作交代。 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191103/60225017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191103%2F60225017&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=927fe9b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191103%2F60225017&h=eab0d02f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191103/60225017</a>"},{"pid":"33187c4b80e82950c3fe898cc5207783a0871945","tid":1689573,"uid":190396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:32:47.000Z","msg":"可以po上微博<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［最新戰術討論］拉一派打一派，分化敵人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689534</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"77225747b95a1001b6ac06375f86bdb6fb632491","tid":1689573,"uid":8392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:35:08.000Z","msg":"即係講國語都打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88395df93c9507c5eeffb96f1bfb2a5db9b28b1e","tid":1689573,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:39:12.000Z","msg":"呵呵好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n物極必反"},{"pid":"1406aad2dd1fc3d80e99d79dcf90c7cff12ad44f","tid":1689573,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:51:14.000Z","msg":"唔知駛唔駛向狗狗道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf8b98a55c37df276b55d8ea7b156d7389ba4ac","tid":1689573,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:58:42.000Z","msg":"大陸女朋友，男係咪香港人無講"}]}